 We can model how many 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsdice{6}$
\end_inset

 are gained by: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{N_{other\rightarrow\epsdice{6}}}{\Delta t}=\alpha\cdot\left(N-N_{\epsdice{6}}\right)\cdot p_{\epsdice{6}}.\label{eq:rsix}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

Before you read further, pause for a moment.
 Can you figure out what this equation does given the definitions of the
 terms above? 
