\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{fair}=-6\times\frac{1}{6}\times log_{2}\left(\frac{1}{6}\right)=2.58\ bits
\]

\end_inset

I know something (the roll has can have six possible outcomes, with equal
 probability for each) but the specific face that will show is uncertain.
